description:
No broker fee!

 Welcome to this converted 2-bedroom apartment in an elevator building with a laundry room and live-in Super, featuring:

 - Super bright Queen-size bedrooms with closets in each;
 - Cozy living room;
 - Open style modern kitchen with a breakfast bar;
 - Fully tiled bathroom with a soaking tub. 

 This pet-friendly building is located at the heart of Financial District with easy commuting options across the City.

EXCEPTIONALLY Large and Spacious 1 Bedroom + sleeping loft GARDEN apartment;
 Four family totally Renovated 1860s Landmark Brownstone featuring: Spacious Living/Dining room, High Ceilings, Track Lighting; Large Garden (shared), plus Private Deck with Carriage Light; Exposed Brick Walls, two non-working Fireplaces; Wood Floors; Two very large Closets with lights in them; Modern Kitchen including ice-maker & microwave; Modern Bath. Apartment is floor-through with lots of light! Landmark tree-lined block!

TEXT OR EMAIL NICOLE FOR FASTEST RESPONSE!
